Package de.iftm.dcm4che.router.plugin

Class Summary
Annotation This class draws annotations on an Graphics2D Object.
DicomRouterPlugin Implements a DicomRouterPlugin.
DicomStorageSCUPlugin This class extends the DicomRouterPlugin class and implements DicomRouterPlugin interface.
ExportImagePlugin This plugins exports the given Dataset as a standard graphic image.
InfoPlugin This plugin logs information of the processed dataset.
NullPlugin This plugin does nothing.
PluginChain This class implements a factory for creating and linking DicomRouterPlugin.
PortableMediaCreatorPlugin This plugins creates a IHE (Integrating the Healthcare Enterprise) PDI (Portable Data for Imaging) compatible file structure (see http://www.rsna.org/IHE/tf/ihe_tf_index.shtml).
PrivateRemovePlugin This removes all private elements of the submitted Dataset.
PseudonymPlugin This plugin replaces the PatientName with a pseudonym.
SaveDicomdirPlugin This plugins saves the given Dataset as a file to the local filesystem and stores a reference to this file in a DICOMDIR index file according DICOM Part 10.
SaveFilesystemPlugin This plugins saves the given Dataset to the lokal filesystem.
TagModifyPlugin This plugin modifies named elements of the submitted Dataset.
UIDModifyPlugin This plugin modifies the UID's.
XSLTransformPlugin This plugins transforms the given Dataset using a XSL document.
